title: Andre's Casino
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Canteen of finance authority, but open for everyone. Serves breakfast and lunch. Offers one vegetarian meal per day, also a large salad plate (can be ordered vegan) is available daily. All side dishes (fries, vegetables, noodles, salad and more) can be ordered ala carte to create a vegan lunch also.
